Package com.yifanlu.Kindle

Interface Summary
Menuable Represents an object that stores menu items.
 

Class Summary
Extension This class represents the extension and is parsed by the config.xml file.
ExtensionsLoader This class holds the functions for loading and parsing the XML configs from extensions.
JARClassLoader This classloader allows loading JARs from any URL and does not require the URL to be passed on initiation.
JSONMenu This class holds the menu options for a JSON menu.
KindleLauncher The main class that is called when the Launcher menu is opened.
KindleLauncherResources Localization for the Launcher menu.
LauncherAction A menu item for Launcher.
LauncherMenu A menu item that contains a submenu.
LauncherScript A menu item that executes a shell command.
ReaderPluginLauncher A Kindle Reader SDK plugin that adds the Launcher menu item to the main Kindle menu.
